commentary: Bishoo to Ahmed Shehzad, OUT Bishoo takes out Shehzad! Another lovely leg break, luring Shehzad forward by the flight, before it dipped and turned away from him. Shehzad wasn't looking for the big hit; he didn't throw his wicket; he was just done in by a good delivery. He leaned forward to just defend but dragged his back foot outside the crease and was done in by the flight, loop, and turn. Stumped!
shortText: Bishoo to Ahmed Shehzad, OUT
text: Bishoo takes out Shehzad! Another lovely leg break, luring Shehzad forward by the flight, before it dipped and turned away from him. Shehzad wasn't looking for the big hit; he didn't throw his wicket; he was just done in by a good delivery. He leaned forward to just defend but dragged his back foot outside the crease and was done in by the flight, loop, and turn. Stumped!
